	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you are a wife, the Father's Heart Bible™ is for you.</strong> You hold a marriage together — the mental load, the meals, the moods, the unspoken hopes — often while quietly wondering if anyone truly sees you. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free on any phone — and it reveals God as <em>Father</em> from Genesis to Revelation. Whether you're searching for "Bible verses for wives," "encouragement for a weary wife," or comfort for marital loneliness, it begins in one place: before you are a wife, you are a beloved daughter — and your Father already calls you His delight.`}
	keyTakeaway={`You cannot give a love you have not first received. Before you are a wife, you are a daughter of God — seen, cherished, and delighted in — so you can love your husband from a full heart, not an empty one.`}
	painsHeading={`The weight wives carry`}
	painsIntroHtml={`Behind the steadiness she gives everyone else, many a wife is carrying more than anyone notices — the invisible planning, the emotional labor, the slow ache of feeling needed but not truly seen. The longing to be cherished is not weakness; it is the cry of a heart made for love. And the research shows just how heavy and lonely that load can quietly become.`}
