		{ ref: `Psalm 45:11`, slug: `psalms`, ch: 45, text: `The King will desire your beauty. Since he is your Lord, bow to him; for you are altogether lovely to the One who made you.`, note: `You are not merely tolerated or needed — you are desired and called lovely by the King who is your Father.` },
