	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet God as Father — and yourself as His daughter`, bodyHtml: `Every other Bible names Him “God.” The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals Him as <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> onward. When God has a Father's face, you stop reading as a tired wife trying harder and start receiving as a beloved daughter being cherished.` },
		{ heading: `It fills the heart you pour from`, bodyHtml: `Free to <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">read online</a> with audio on every chapter, it's made for a wife's real day — listen while you fold laundry or drive carpool, and let your Father love you before you give yourself away again. You love your husband best from a full heart, not an empty one.` },
